snippet.title: Framed Collection Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The FRAMED Collection is a compilation of the critically acclaimed, multi-award winning, noir-puzzle games FRAMED and FRAMED 2, where you re-arrange panels of an animated comic book to change the outcome of the story. 

Wishlist it now on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/322450/FRAMED_Collection/
